title: Adam Gold on Jalen Ramsey's QB comments (Football 08/16)
description:
Will Brinson breaks down the latest news and notes from around the NFL before being joined by Adam Gold of 99.9 The Fan in Raleigh to hammer out takes on Jalen Ramsey's takes about quarterbacks around the NFL. Is Josh Allen trash? Does Joe Flacco suck? WHO IS MATT RYAN? The guys answer all of these very important questions and much more.
